# Sam Goddard — Media Scaling & Attention Monetization

The operating system behind scaling a founder's personal brand from niche expert to media empire. Sam Goddard built Dan Martell from 100K niche SaaS followers to 9M+ across platforms with 200M+ monthly views — then architected the monetization layer that turned that attention into Martell Ventures and an AI Incubator.

## Core Domain

Content operations at scale, phased media team building, retention-first scripting, attention-to-revenue architecture, audience aperture widening, decade-frame strategic planning.

## What Makes This Skill Different

Most personal brand skills focus on **content creation** (what to post, how to write hooks). This skill operates at the **systems layer** — how to build the team, scale the operation, engineer retention, and monetize attention at venture-scale. It's the difference between being a content creator and running a media company.

## Deployable Capabilities

### Operations Layer (7 prompts)

| Capability | Prompt | Use When |
|-----------|--------|----------|
| Widen audience without losing identity | `aperture-widening-strategy` | Brand has maxed its niche, needs to 10x audience |
| Design phased media team build | `gopro-scaling-blueprint` | Creator ready to move from solo to professional operation |
| Engineer content retention | `retention-reframe-engineering` | Scripting any long-form content — YouTube, podcast, webinar |
| Calculate organic vs paid ROI | `attention-arbitrage-calculator` | Evaluating content investment economics |
| Evaluate content writers | `scriptwriter-reframe-test` | Hiring writers, QA'ing scripts before production |
| Design attention → revenue pipeline | `attention-monetization-architect` | Creator/founder with audience wondering how to monetize beyond courses |
| Evaluate decisions across decades | `decade-frame-strategy` | Any major brand/business/partnership decision |

### Content Philosophy Layer (7 prompts)

| Capability | Prompt | Use When |
|-----------|--------|----------|
| Map interest-based topics with Three-Circle Venn | `interest-demand-mapper` | Selecting topics that cut through algorithmic noise with Fit + Interest + Demand |
| Run internal/external research + indirect interpretation | `trend-research-system` | Finding demand pockets via Google Trends, research accounts, outlier analysis |
| Build Title + Thumbnail + Promise before scripting | `concept-promise-architect` | Pre-production concept lock — the "offer" of the video |
| Create real-person character profiles for every script | `subtext-character-builder` | Writing content that talks to ONE person so it resonates with millions |
| Engineer reframes, USPs, and retention mechanisms | `unique-mechanism-engineer` | Differentiating content from competitors + building aha moments |
| Design burnout-proof content operation | `sustainable-creator-blueprint` | Creator approaching burnout, needs system that works for 20+ years |
| Produce shoot-ready outline scripts with AI checklist | `script-production-system` | Complete scriptwriting from concept → outline → fundamentals check |

## Workflow Decision Tree

```
Need to scale audience?
├── Niche ceiling hit? → aperture-widening-strategy
├── Need to build team? → gopro-scaling-blueprint
└── Not sure if organic investment is worth it? → attention-arbitrage-calculator

Need to create content?
├── What topics to make? → interest-demand-mapper
├── Finding demand pockets? → trend-research-system
├── Pre-production concept lock? → concept-promise-architect
├── Who am I writing for? → subtext-character-builder
├── How do I differentiate? → unique-mechanism-engineer
├── Full script production? → script-production-system
└── Scripts need more retention? → retention-reframe-engineering

Need to sustain/scale?
├── Approaching burnout? → sustainable-creator-blueprint
├── Evaluating writers? → scriptwriter-reframe-test
└── Big strategic decision? → decade-frame-strategy

Need to monetize?
├── Have audience, unsure how to extract value? → attention-monetization-architect
└── Not sure if organic investment is worth it? → attention-arbitrage-calculator
```

## Quick Start

1. **If you have a content brand**: Run `attention-arbitrage-calculator` to see your real content ROI
2. **If you're hiring writers**: Run `scriptwriter-reframe-test` on their samples
3. **If you're stuck at niche audience size**: Run `aperture-widening-strategy` to find your expansion path

